        <div class="ma-use-card">
          <div class="ma-use-idx">01</div>
          <h3>Operations Automation</h3>
          <p>Remove manual steps, reduce errors, and speed up routine work with intelligent process automation.</p>
          <div class="ma-use-tags">
            <span>Python</span><span>OCR</span><span>Workflows</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-use-card">
          <div class="ma-use-idx">02</div>
          <h3>Data &amp; Reporting</h3>
          <p>Bring data together and give teams clear dashboards, alerts, and actionable insights.</p>
          <div class="ma-use-tags">
            <span>Analytics</span><span>Dashboards</span><span>APIs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-use-card">
          <div class="ma-use-idx">03</div>
          <h3>AI Assistants for Teams</h3>
          <p>Turn meetings and messages into organised tasks, updates, and automated workflows.</p>
          <div class="ma-use-tags">
            <span>NLP</span><span>Agents</span><span>Integration</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="ma-section ma-section-alt" id="process">
    <div class="ma-container">
      <div class="ma-section-header">
        <span class="ma-section-tag">// process</span>
        <h2>Our 5-stage development process</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="ma-process">
        <div class="ma-process-step">
          <div class="ma-process-num">01</div>
          <div class="ma-process-content">
            <h3>Discovery</h3>
            <p>Understand your challenge, map processes, identify highest-value opportunity.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-process-step">
          <div class="ma-process-num">02</div>
          <div class="ma-process-content">
            <h3>Proof of Concept</h3>
            <p>Build a focused prototype to validate approach and demonstrate feasibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-process-step">
          <div class="ma-process-num">03</div>
          <div class="ma-process-content">
            <h3>MVP</h3>
            <p>Develop a working product with core features ready for real-world testing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-process-step">
          <div class="ma-process-num">04</div>
          <div class="ma-process-content">
            <h3>Pilot</h3>
            <p>Deploy with a controlled group, gather feedback, refine before wider rollout.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-process-step">
          <div class="ma-process-num">05</div>
          <div class="ma-process-content">
            <h3>Full Launch</h3>
            <p>Scale to production with monitoring, support, and continuous improvement.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Studies -->
  <section class="ma-section" id="work">
    <div class="ma-container">
      <div class="ma-section-header">
        <span class="ma-section-tag">// case_studies</span>
        <h2>Recent work</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="ma-cases">
        <div class="ma-case">
          <div class="ma-case-header">
            <span class="ma-case-badge">Manufacturing</span>
            <span class="ma-case-result">Hours → Minutes</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Automating Surface Area Calculations for Protective Coatings</h3>
          <p>Transformed hours of manual PDF analysis into minutes with 100% calculation accuracy. OCR-enabled tagging interface with automated Excel report generation.</p>
          <div class="ma-case-stack">
            <span>Python</span><span>Flask/FastAPI</span><span>React</span><span>MongoDB</span><span>OCR</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-case">
          <div class="ma-case-header">
            <span class="ma-case-badge">Manufacturing</span>
            <span class="ma-case-result">Zero Missed Tasks</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Intelligent Maintenance Management via Mobile Messaging</h3>
          <p>Messaging-native AI agent for production floor engineers. Natural language processing, voice notes, and photo capture — no training required.</p>
          <div class="ma-case-stack">
            <span>AI Agent</span><span>NLP</span><span>Cloud APIs</span><span>Mobile</span><span>Voice</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ma-case">
          <div class="ma-case-header">
            <span class="ma-case-badge">Infrastructure</span>
            <span class="ma-case-result">Accelerated Delivery</span>
          </div>
          <h3>AI/ML Expertise as Technical Subcontractor</h3>
          <p>Delivered vector database architecture, ML pipelines, and conversational AI within a consultancy's infrastructure monitoring project.</p>
          <div class="ma-case-stack">
            <span>Vector DB</span><span>ML</span><span>Gen AI</span><span>NLP</span><span>APIs</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="ma-section ma-section-alt" id="faq">
    <div class="ma-container ma-faq-wrap">
      <div class="ma-section-header">
        <span class="ma-section-tag">// faq</span>
        <h2>Common questions</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="ma-faq-list">
        <details class="ma-faq-item">
          <summary>How long does a typical engagement take?</summary>
          <p>Discovery takes 1–2 weeks. A Proof of Concept typically follows in 4–6 weeks. The full timeline depends on scope, but our staged approach means you see results early.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ma-faq-item">
          <summary>Do you work with existing systems?</summary>
          <p>Yes. We integrate with your current tools, platforms, and data sources. We're stack-agnostic and work with whatever fits your infrastructure and policies.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ma-faq-item">
          <summary>What industries do you work with?</summary>
          <p>We've delivered solutions across manufacturing, infrastructure, energy, and professional services. Our process applies to any sector where AI can streamline operations.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="ma-faq-item">
          <summary>How is pricing structured?</summary>
          <p>Each stage is priced independently so you can validate value before committing to the next. No big-bang contracts — you stay in control throughout.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ma-cta" id="contact">
    <div class="ma-container ma-cta-inner">
      <h2>Ready to see what AI can do<br/>for your business?</h2>
      <p>Book a free discovery call. No obligation, no sales pitch.</p>
      <a href="https://outlook.office.com/bookwithme/user/f0762b9af6a94ed2add9818a4f3ca4e5@digitaltechnologypartner.ai/meetingtype/qc2lOXjEdkO6GkMS_jZJrQ2?anonymous" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="ma-btn ma-btn-mint ma-btn-lg">Book a Discovery Call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="ma-footer">
    <div class="ma-container ma-footer-inner">
      <p>&copy; 2025 Digital Technology Partner. All Rights Reserved.</p>
      <div class="ma-footer-links">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/dtp-ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="mailto:Info@digitaltechnologypartner.ai">Email</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/447769386204">WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Design Variant Badge -->
  <div class="ma-variant-badge">
    V2: Midnight Authority
    <a href="/design-v1">← Prev</a>
    <a href="/design-v3">Next →</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  /* ========== V2: MIDNIGHT AUTHORITY ========== */
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ma-bg: #0A0A0F;
    --ma-surface: #1A1A2E;
    --ma-surface-alt: #111122;
    --ma-border: #2A2A3E;
    --ma-mint: #00E5A0;
    --ma-mint-dim: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.12);
    --ma-text: #E0E0E0;
    --ma-text-dim: #8888A0;
    --ma-white: #F0F0F5;
    --ma-font-display: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    --ma-font-body: 'IBM Plex Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  .ma-body {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-body);
    background: var(--ma-bg);
    color: var(--ma-text);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 16px;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .ma-container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }

  /* --- NAV --- */
  .ma-nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(10, 10, 15, 0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ma-border);
  }

  .ma-nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 68px;
  }

  .ma-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ma-logo-img {
    height: 32px;
    width: auto;
  }

  .ma-nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2rem; }

  .ma-nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ma-text-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 200ms ease;
  }

  .ma-nav-links a:hover { color: var(--ma-mint); }

  .ma-nav-cta { font-size: 0.82rem !important; padding: 0.45rem 1.1rem !important; }

  /* --- BUTTONS --- */
  .ma-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: all 220ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .ma-btn-mint {
    background: var(--ma-mint);
    color: #0A0A0F;
  }

  .ma-btn-mint:hover {
    background: #00ffb3;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.35);
  }

  .ma-btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ma-text);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ma-border);
  }

  .ma-btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--ma-mint);
    color: var(--ma-mint);
  }

  .ma-btn-lg { font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.95rem 2rem; }

  /* --- HERO --- */
  .ma-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 11rem 0 6rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ma-hero-grid-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--ma-border) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ma-border) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 60px 60px;
    opacity: 0.15;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 70% at 50% 40%, black, transparent);
  }

  .ma-hero-scan {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--ma-mint), transparent);
    opacity: 0.5;
    animation: ma-scan 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes ma-scan {
    0% { top: 10%; opacity: 0; }
    10% { opacity: 0.5; }
    90% { opacity: 0.5; }
    100% { top: 95%; opacity: 0; }
  }

  .ma-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 720px; }

  .ma-hero-tag {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ma-mint);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .ma-hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--ma-white);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ma-cursor {
    color: var(--ma-mint);
    animation: ma-blink 1s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes ma-blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  .ma-hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--ma-text-dim);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .ma-hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 4rem; }

  .ma-hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ma-border);
  }

  .ma-stat-val {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ma-mint);
  }

  .ma-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--ma-text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .ma-stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--ma-border);
  }

  /* --- SECTIONS --- */
  .ma-section { padding: 6rem 0; }
  .ma-section-alt { background: var(--ma-surface-alt); }

  .ma-section-header { margin-bottom: 3.5rem; }

  .ma-section-tag {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--ma-mint);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .ma-section-header h2 {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ma-white);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  /* --- CARDS GRID --- */
  .ma-grid-6 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .ma-card {
    background: var(--ma-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--ma-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.75rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ma-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--ma-mint);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--ma-mint), 0 16px 40px rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.08);
  }

  .ma-card-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--ma-mint), transparent);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 250ms ease;
  }

  .ma-card:hover .ma-card-line { opacity: 1; }

  .ma-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ma-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ma-card p { color: var(--ma-text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  /* --- TESTIMONIAL --- */
  .ma-testimonial {
    max-width: 720px;
    position: relative;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .ma-quote-mark {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: 6rem;
    color: var(--ma-mint);
    opacity: 0.15;
    position: absolute;
    top: -1rem;
    left: -0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ma-testimonial blockquote {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--ma-white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .ma-testimonial cite {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--ma-text-dim);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* --- USE CASES --- */
  .ma-use-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ma-use-card {
    background: var(--ma-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--ma-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 250ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .ma-use-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.4);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .ma-use-idx {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ma-mint);
    opacity: 0.2;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ma-use-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--ma-font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ma-white);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .ma-use-card p { color: var(--ma-text-dim); font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }

  .ma-use-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  .ma-use-tags span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--ma-mint-dim);
    color: var(--ma-mint);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* --- PROCESS --- */
  .ma-process {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--ma-border);
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .ma-process-step {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem 0 1.5rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 250ms ease;
  }

  .ma-process-step:hover { background: rgba(0, 229, 160, 0.03); }

  .ma-process-step::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -7px;
